    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>--故事模式&amp;挑战模式--</i></strong></h2><br><strong>这是一款基于UE4引擎打造的卡通渲染风格剧情×三消游戏。在游戏中，你将跟随着角色们前往一个个平行宇宙，你所做出的每个选择都将影响游戏的结局。</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >角色介绍</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/4192cae7686d8c7b911224f464102616.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=368 height=593 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/4192cae7686d8c7b911224f464102616.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>艾薇·特里特</strong></i><br>由人类富家大小姐变为的吸血鬼，在庄园中独自一人寂寞地度过了六十年的时光。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/2747c09196414e5a1e4f5dc6b9f76544.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=250 height=612 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/2747c09196414e5a1e4f5dc6b9f76544.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>丽蓓卡·芬格莱特</strong></i><br>血族公主，纯种吸血鬼，喜欢捉弄他人的命运论者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/0415f496daad2c5d001b352b3babf254.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=139 height=582 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/0415f496daad2c5d001b352b3babf254.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>实习生丽塔</strong></i><br>联邦研究保护局C级人员，年轻一代著名的天才。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/e2a5cc7384fb7598b69ccdecbb2de448.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=332 height=628 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/e2a5cc7384fb7598b69ccdecbb2de448.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>琳</strong></i><br>出生在极北之地的龙族少女，受母亲霜龙族长之命作为使者常居在人类王宫内。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/ad1d413370288b01e1bfb38dde2cc66e.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=293 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/ad1d413370288b01e1bfb38dde2cc66e.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>伊欧娜</strong></i><br>曾经的女公爵，联合王国现任女王。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/13ff9f86205acd16c9bde508055c2382.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=500 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/13ff9f86205acd16c9bde508055c2382.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>彩云</strong></i><br>跨越时间长河的存在，永远停留在年轻岁月的小僵尸。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/8b54da4acdf4b29650bcd429b7868dab.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=250 height=427 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/8b54da4acdf4b29650bcd429b7868dab.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>窦倩兮</strong></i><br>出身大户人家的千金小姐。自幼在书香门第的环境中长大，却偏爱研究天工机械的大家闺秀。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/d8a01b680dc0524d35c89b4eddb0b5e1.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=246 height=594 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/d8a01b680dc0524d35c89b4eddb0b5e1.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>菈妮</strong></i><br>原始部落居民，末世中的流浪者<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/ed5fba944556a09c56581c20a4c3b395.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=435 height=529 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/ed5fba944556a09c56581c20a4c3b395.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><i>莉娅</i></strong><br>联邦研究保护局1级收容物，来源未知，目的未知，年龄未知。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/ffc7c3bb598b9d7636963de4deefd869.poster.avif?t=1673932541\" width=274 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832640/extras/ffc7c3bb598b9d7636963de4deefd869.webm?t=1673932541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong><i>丽塔</i></strong><br>女博士，联邦研究保护局高级干部，超自然生物研究所的技术负责人。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>随着剧情的推进你需要在很多节点做出选择，不同的选择将会进入不同的故事线。剧情要如何推进，选择完全在你手中。<br><br>在剧情中还会有益智小游戏需要玩家完成解密，把三个颜色相同的物品连成一条直线即可消除。在一定回合限制内，达到指定的目标即可通关解锁新剧情分支。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>宏大的世界观，让你沉浸其中不能自拔。<br></li><li>如现实存在一般的，真实的角色构建，让你有动力深入探索每个角色的故事。<br></li><li>你的任何选择都将决定游戏剧情的走向。存在还是毁灭，选择只在你手中。<br></li><li>继承前作爽快轻松的益智三消模式，全新3D画面，特效升级。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>--家园模式--</i></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏介绍</h2><br>终于可以休息一下了，你带着的美少女们，开始了一段奇妙而美好的度假时光。<br>阳光、海水、沙滩，你可以与他们一起，尽情享受多黛海岛的美丽风光；<br>泳池、浴室、床，你也可以为他们，拍摄各种性感的照片；<br>美丽的海岛上，处处都值得探索，快跟美少女们一起，尽情享受假日的温馨和浪漫吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>精致唯美的全3D二次元角色和场景<br></li><li>多个mirror美少女角色期待与你邂逅<br></li><li>多种不同的服装造型和饰品随心搭配<br></li><li>多种不同的交互场景等你发掘<br></li><li>多个控制节点，DIY你想要的各种姿势。<br></li><li>开放<u><strong>Steam创意工坊</strong></u>，大家一起自由创造吧</li></ul><br><br>我们的星辰大海：<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>更丰富的mirror角色及饰品，尽情装扮他们吧<br></li><li>更开阔的场景，更丰富的互动地点及互动内容，尽享多黛海岛带来的快乐<br></li><li>更简单便捷的姿势编辑，支持自定义导入角色及动画，让你随时随地DIY<br></li><li>支持<u><strong>VR设备</strong></u>接入，让你身临其境，与美少女们一同狂欢</li></ul>",
